g decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1698\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-1186x1536.jpg 1186w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-1581x2048.jpg 1581w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1698px) 100vw, 1698px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201698%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-1186x1536.jpg 1186w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-1581x2048.jpg 1581w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo I started making cheeseburger lettuce wraps. Dreamy. And so easy. The lettuce wraps add this cooling, refreshing bite on a hot summer day. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1729\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-scaled.jpg 1729w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-728x926.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-768x977.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-1610x2048.jpg 1610w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1729px) 100vw, 1729px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201729%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-scaled.jpg 1729w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-728x926.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-768x977.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-1610x2048.jpg 1610w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow here is why THESE burgers are the best: \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThey are topped with blue cheese which gets extra melty. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCaramelized onions, which we know make every burger better.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd a drizzle of creamy homemade honey mustard! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll wrapped up in that cold iceberg lettuce leaf. Juicy as heck, melty with cheese, so flavorful I could scream. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99163\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1695\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-scaled.jpg 1695w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-728x945.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-768x997.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-1183x1536.jpg 1183w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-1578x2048.jpg 1578w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-150x195.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1695px) 100vw, 1695px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201695%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-scaled.jpg 1695w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-728x945.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-768x997.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-1183x1536.jpg 1183w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-1578x2048.jpg 1578w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-150x195.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe key with these burgers is making them how YOU like them. Add as much blue cheese as you’d like. Or heck, use cheddar. I will use one or two pieces of lettuce, depending on the size of the leaves and the size of the burgers. Make the burgers smaller or large, based on your preference. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAdd as many caramelized onions on top as you wish! Drizzle with honey mustard or use another condiment of your choice. There is no wrong way here and that’s the exciting part. This is more of a guide of how to make a delicious caramelized onion burger in a lettuce wrap. Yum yum yum. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1677\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-scaled.jpg 1677w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-728x955.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-768x1007.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-1171x1536.jpg 1171w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-1561x2048.jpg 1561w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-12-150x197.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1677px) 100vw, 1677px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDreamboat!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1720\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-768x983.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1720px) 100vw, 1720px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201720%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-768x983.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eLettuce Wrap Blue Cheese Burgers with Caramelized Onions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99177\" data-recipe-id=\"99177\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-11-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eLettuce Wrap Blue Cheese Burgers with Caramelized Onions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99177\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 6\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003cspan\u003e hours\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003cspan\u003e hours\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan\u003e20\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThese lettuce wrap burgers are my new favorite burger! Melty blue cheese burgers topped with tons of caramelized onions, a drizzle of creamy honey mustard all wrapped in a lettuce cup. Refreshing, satisfying and crisp!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99177\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elarge sweet onions,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ethinly sliced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/salted-butter-1lb-good-gather-8482/-/A-54445965?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebutter\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/73-27-ground-beef-1lb-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-17294006?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003elean ground beef\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecrumbled blue cheese,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehead iceberg lettuce,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eleaves pulled off and washed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2 to 3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped fresh chives,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99177\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the butter in a large skillet over medium heat. Once melted, stir in the onions with a big pinch of salt and pepper and the thyme. Cook for 10 to 12 minutes, stirring often, until the onions begin to soften. Turn the heat down to low and cook, stirring often, until the onions are dark brown and caramely, anywhere from 1 to 2 hours, or until the onions reach the color you desire.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis will take a while and the onions are apt to burn. Keep an eye on them and stir often, reducing the heat when needed. Add a splash of water to the pan if it gets too dry at any time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo make the burgers, season the ground beef well with salt and pepper. Divide the beef into 4 or 6 patties - depending on how large you want them. It’s up to you! I prefer a thinner patty, so I usually make 6 thinner burger patties.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can use the same skillet you cooked the onions in or use a new one. Heat the skillet over medium heat and add a small drizzle of olive oil if needed. Add the burger patties and cook until deeply golden. Flip the burger. Top with a few spoonfuls of the crumbled blue cheese (as much as you’d like!) and let the other side brown and the cheese melts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eServe the burgers on the lettuce cups. Depending on the lettuce, I will use 1 or 2 pieces per burger. Top each burger with caramelized onions. Drizzle on the honey mustard and sprinkle on the chives. Serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003ecreamy honey mustard\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99177-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhisk together until smooth and combined. Store in the fridge in a sealed container.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lettuce wrap burgers with caramelized onions\" width=\"1638\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lettuce Wrap Blue CheeseBurgers with Caramelized Onions.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/lettuce-wrap-burgers-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://ww